  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of Single Port Laparoscopic Appendectomy in Acute Appendicitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective, Randomized Study of Single Port and Conventional Laparoscopic Appendectomy in Acute Appendicitis</official_title>
